@startuml CompletarFormulario
title Diagrama de Secuencia - Completar Formulario

actor Cliente
participant "Microsoft Forms" as Forms
participant "CompletarFormularioFlow" as Flow
participant "Formulario" as Formulario
database "Power BI" as PowerBI

Cliente -> Forms : completarFormulario(datos)
Forms -> Flow : enviarRespuestas(datos)
Flow -> Formulario : crearFormulario(datos)
Formulario --> Flow : formularioCreado
Flow -> PowerBI : registrarFormulario(formulario)
PowerBI --> Flow : registroConfirmado

@enduml